My uncle, and brother carry alot of unnesessary guilt to this day thinking that they could have stopped it from happening as my brother was in my dads until 6.30 pm on this birthday and my uncle went to my dads door about an hour after my brother left but when he was at the door he heard arguing so decided just to go home and go see him the next day. I got a phone call from a friend who lived on the same floor as my dad the morning after it happend.
